'''Lev Alekseyev''' (born 18 April 1926) is a [[Russia]]n former [[Sailing (sport)|sailor]] who competed in the [[1952 Summer Olympics]], in the [[1956 Summer Olympics]], and in the [[1964 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=sref>{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/al/lev-alekseyev-1.html |accessdate=2 July 2012}}</ref>
